'''恒河宫河坛'''（Ganga Mahal Ghat，[[印地语|印地语]]：गंगा महल घाट）是印度[[瓦拉纳西|瓦拉纳西]][[恒河|恒河]]岸边的主要河坛之一。由纳拉扬王朝建于公元1830年，它位于[[阿西河坛|阿西河坛]]以北100米<ref name="Location">{{cite news|title=Location|publisher=Google Maps|accessdate=Sep 2015|url=https://www.google.co.uk/maps|archive-date=2015-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150812173936/https://www.google.co.uk/maps|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最初是作为对阿西河坛的延伸。<ref name="Ganga Mahal Ghat">{{cite news|title=Ganga Mahal Ghat|publisher=Varanasi.nic.in|accessdate=Sep 2015|url=http://varanasi.nic.in/ghat/ghat1-20.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113184526/http://varanasi.nic.in/ghat/ghat1-20.html|archive-date=2012-11-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Ghats of Varanasi">{{cite news|title=Ghats of Varanasi|publisher=Varanasi.org|accessdate=Sep 2015|url=http://www.varanasi.org.in/ghats-of-varanasi|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118202804/https://www.varanasi.org.in/ghats-of-varanasi|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="About Ghats">{{cite news|title=About Ghats|publisher=kashiyana.com|accessdate=Sep 2015|url=http://www.kashiyana.com/pages/rghat.aspx?id1=20150117050541&id=0|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160809170920/http://www.kashiyana.com/pages/rghat.aspx?id1=20150117050541&id=0|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="The Varanasi Heritage Dossier">{{cite news|title=The Varanasi Heritage Dossier|publisher=Wikiversity|accessdate=Sep 2015|url=https://en.wikiversity.org/wiki/The_Varanasi_Heritage_Dossier/Ganga_Mahala_and_Rivan_Ghat|archive-date=2019-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025060927/https://en.wikiversity.org/wiki/The_Varanasi_Heritage_Dossier/Ganga_Mahala_and_Rivan_Ghat|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
1830年，纳拉扬王朝在瓦拉纳西[[恒河|恒河]]岸边建造了一座宫殿，称为恒河宫（Ganga Mahal）。宫殿所在的河坛便命名为恒河宫河坛。[[阿西河坛|阿西河坛]]和恒河宫河坛之间以石阶分隔成两个河坛。这个宫殿现在作为教育机构使用。一楼用作“加拿大世界扫盲计划”，而上层 则由[[卡尔斯塔德大学|卡尔斯塔德大学]]组织的“印尼 - 瑞典研究中心”使用。<ref name="Ganga Mahal Ghat"/><ref name="Ghats of Varanasi"/><ref name="About Ghats"/><ref name="The Varanasi Heritage Dossier"/>

